cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent

  • Packages that use cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent 
    Package Description
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent
    Package that implements the agent and all the necessary classes, that let the user control it.
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.graphics
    Package containing all the graphics we use.
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.interests
    Package that defines classes that represents important places on the in-game map.
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.server
    This package implements the HTTP server (using Jetty) and classes that are used to handle the communication with dot2ai addon.
    cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world
    This package represents the world.
